~ start
I am a native from this archipelago.
Do you want to hear my story?
- Yes => help_accepted
- No => help_denied

~ help_accepted
Lore lore lore.
Bye!
do GameState.global.helper.clear()
=> END

~ help_denied
OK, bye!
=> END
